info.title: Spacebar Server
info.description: Spacebar is a Discord.com server implementation and extension, with the goal of complete feature parity with Discord.com, all while adding some additional goodies, security, privacy, and configuration options.

Network.Headers.description: Request / response headers as keys / values of JSON object.

Snowflake.description: A container for useful snowflake-related methods.

reload.description: Reloads entity data from the database.

hasId.description:
Checks if entity has an id.
If entity composite compose ids, it will check them all.

save.description:
Saves current entity in the database.
If entity does not exist in the database then inserts, otherwise updates.

remove.description: Removes current entity from the database.

softRemove.description: Records the delete date of current entity.

recover.description: Recovers a given entity in the database.

get.description: Returns a list of channel webhook objects. Requires the MANAGE_WEBHOOKS permission.

parameters.name: limit
parameters.description: max number of messages to return (1-100). defaults to 50

parameters.name: count
parameters.description: The number of registration tokens to generate. Defaults to 1.

parameters.name: length
parameters.description: The length of each registration token. Defaults to 255.
